Lawa madoda aneminyaka ephakathi kwewu-22 kuya ku-30 kusolwa ukuthi ahlasela uMnuz Lwandile Tenza (19) nomngani wakhe ngoDisemba 21. Kuthiwa amadoda amahlanu aphuca amadoda amabili amaselula ngesikhathi ewahlasela. Kuthiwa umngani kamufi wakwazi ukubaleka wayobika ngokubehlele. Kwase kuvulwa icala lokulahleka kukamufi, obekungaziwa ukuthi washonaphi ngemuva kokubanjwa inkunzi. Okhulumela amaphoyisa KwaZulu-Natal, uCapt Nqobile Gwala, uthe amaphoyisa ayesebenza endaweni abikelwa ngesidumbu okuthiwa sibonakale sintanta edamini uMzimkhulwana elikhona endaweni, anikela khona. Isidumbu sabonwa ukuthi ngesikamufi. “Kusolwa ukuthi abasolwa bambulala umufi base bemphonsa edamini. Amaphoyisa abe eseqhubeka nophenyo lwawo, oluholele ekutheni abophe amadoda amahlanu ayamaniswa nokubulawa kowesilisa ngoMsombuluko. Abasolwa baboshelwe icala lokubulala nelokubamba inkunzi,” uGwala. Uthe kulindeleke ukuthi abasolwa bavele eNkantolo yeMantshi eMzimkhulu maduze.